latestIgtvVideos.title: Hair tutorial and Raw Sugar Hair care review
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It’s time to #letyourhairdown ! 🥥 today I review two @rawsugarliving hair care products- the Moisture Smoothie and the Bounce Back 💁‍♀️ all while showing your how I style my hair 💕 even better @target is offering a $5 Gift Card if you purchase 4 Raw Sugar Hair Care Products, offer is valid from July 28th to August 3rd!
.
.
.
The Moisture smoothie is enriched with Certified Organic extracts to give your dehydrated hair an infusion of moisture and shine. Coconut delivers pure hydration, Agave helps restore shine, and protein-rich Almond Milk smooths frizz. 🥥 
The Bounce Back is enriched with Certified Organic extracts to give your hair weightless body and bounce. 🥭Mango Butter delivers ultra-softening benefits, Agave helps restore shine, and Carrot Oil stimulates growth by strengthening the roots. 🥕 .
.
.
To make things even sweeter for every product that you purchase, Raw Sugar donates a fresh bar of soap to a family in need’ it’s beauty you can truly feel good about!
